    "long_instructions": "Some `Painter`s have been given instructions to go to the house party, but the `Painter`s haven't been created yet!\r\n\r\nFix the program by creating more `Painter`s.\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/4eb615dcfa692c69948b993e4e24b34c-choiceA.gif)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<i class=\"fa-solid fa-laptop\"></i> **Coding Tip**\r\n\r\nTo create a `Painter`, use\r\n\r\n   ```\r\n   painter_name = Painter()\r\n   ```\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n   ```\r\n   alicia = Painter()\r\n   ```",
